title: Ciboulette 6
description: Ciboulette (French chives) are known in culinary for its fresh, mild onion-like flavor and are employed in many dishes throughout the world. This palette captures the greenery of the leaves, the brown dirt and the delicate pink flowers to compose a pastel-like, well-rounded palette which goes well with mellow, natural compositions but will also work for slimes and grime.
